data.description: New construction home w/ easy commute to the metro area. Just 20 min from LRAFB. The 4 bed 2 bath home features a split floorplan w/the master separate from other bedrooms. The kitchen has stainless appliances, large island, pantry, granite countertops, eat in area plus a dining room w/doors that could be used as an office or bonus area. The master bath has dbl vanities & both walk in tiled shower & soaking tub. Home will be complete by July. Pictures are of like home to show floorplan and finishes.
